product.shortDescription: Barbie Color Reveal dolls deliver an unboxing experience with seven surprises, including a scented Barbie doll covered in a mixed fruit coating whose look is revealed with water! With the Sweet Fruit Series, kids will find one of five possible dolls, each with a fruity scent like cherries, watermelon, strawberries, pineapple and citrus lemon, plus fruit-themed clothes and accessories hidden in the four mystery bags. Color-change effects on Barbie dolls eyes and lips add more wow. Kids can look for the rare doll that comes with a bonus purse and bright pink hair extension for even more mixing and matching! Use the packaging tube to store these and other accessories. Which doll will you reveal? Each sold separately, subject to availability. Dolls cannot stand alone. Colors and decorations may vary.

product.name: Barbie Color Reveal Scented Sweet Fruit Fashion Doll with Accessories & Color Change (Styles May Vary)

chokingHazards.headline: CHOKING HAZARD - Children Under 3
chokingHazards.message: This toy is not suitable for ages under 3 years. It contains one or more of the following items: marbles, small ball, or small parts.

idml.longDescription:
• With 7 surprises in 1 package, the Barbie Color Reveal dolls deliver all kinds of delight -- kids will have fun revealing the Sweet Fruit Series with Original Color Reveal Innovation!
  • Start the reveal experience by removing the outer layer of packaging, opening the tube and pulling out a Barbie doll whose look is covered in a Color Reveal mixed-fruit print coating and 4 decorated bags with hidden contents!
  • Fill the tube with warm water, place the doll inside and swirl around -- the water turns a pretty purple for a magical effect!
  • Pull out the doll to reveal the look -- each doll in the series has long colorful hair, a patterned bodice and a sweet fruit scent. Possibilities include cherry, strawberry, watermelon, citrus lemon and pineapple
  • Open the 4 mystery bags to reveal their surprises -- a top and skirt with matching fruit print, a pair of shoes, a pair of sunglasses and a necklace; store them in the tube after play!
  • Use icy cold and warm water for a color-change transformation that can be repeated over and over again -- change the dolls eyeshadow and lip color!
  • Kids can look for the rare Color Reveal Sweet Fruit Barbie doll who has a pineapple purse and bright pink hair extension!
  • Makes a great gift for kids 3 years and older, who can collect them to mix and match accessories and expand the playtime opportunities!

customerReviews.reviewText: [This review was collected as part of a promotion.] My daughter loved she could change the color of this doll. She even loved that you could just fill the tube it comes in with water, and didnt have to figure out a way to change it. The accessories were super cute as well. She has not stopped playing with it since we got it.

[This review was collected as part of a promotion.] The color reveal doll is perfect for those kids who like messy fun. The upside is that this doll doesnt make a mess! It is nicely packaged and comes with surprises that are perfect for satisfying that craving for opening up little presents. It ALSO comes with its own tub to wash the surprise paint off with. It is the best of both worlds: child feels like they are being messy  but the clean up is so easy and no mess! The doll I have smells like strawberries and has makeup that can appear with cold water. They were hoping the bathing suit changed colors in water, but it doesnt. Maybe that can be the next idea because they really like color change things. This is a great toy and is perfect for a gift.

[This review was collected as part of a promotion.] My daughter Loves the Barbie Color Reveal Doll. The doll comes in a clear tube with surprise accessories, clothes, necklace, and shoes. The doll came with a purple outfit printed on her that body but when the doll is submerged in warm water the print disappeared to reveal a natural skin color her body. The clear tube is filled with water to change Barbies color, Very cool.
customerReviews.reviewTitle: Barbie Color reveal doll is a super fun surprise.

customerReviews.reviewText: [This review was collected as part of a promotion.] My daughter thought this was so much fun. She loved surprise reveal of the Barbie and the accessories. The packaging shows the possible Barbies that you can get and she had fun trying to guess which Barbie it was as we waited for the water to reveal the barbie and she opened the accessories. We did the reveal on a day that she was off from school to add some excitement to the day. The only issue we had was that some of the color on the barbie seemed like it was on thicker in some places and took some extra scrubbing to get all the color off, even after a long soak.
customerReviews.reviewTitle: Fun Barbie with a hint of surprise

customerReviews.reviewText:
Perfect for kids to play with! They have a painted swimsuit for the beach of the swimming pool and extra clothes to go shopping or to stay at home and invite friends.
And fun collecting them :-)

[This review was collected as part of a promotion.] Color reveal Barbies are always a hit in our household! Not only does it contain a classic and fun barbie, but the added bonus of waiting to reveal what we get is so fun for everyone! I definitely recommend as a fun gift for your little!

[This review was collected as part of a promotion.] These color reveal Barbies are always a hit for my 5 year old. She loves a good surprise toy and I love that these have the great quality you can expect from the Barbie brand. I also love that it comes with the perfect size container to do your color reveal! Great toy highly recommend!

[This review was collected as part of a promotion.] My daughter loved the water/color reveal part of this Barbie doll. We were not sure at first why she felt so sticky and then after the water turned purple and we took her out, we realized that the sticky stuff washes away to reveal the doll. She was fun for the reveal and opening all the clothing pieces, but after shes been dressed and played with for a few minutes my daughter hasnt used her any more than any other Barbie doll. The color reveal part is just once and then its done. Her face makeup does change in hot/cold but we tried just rubbing her with a wash rag with hot/cold water and couldnt get her face to change. We had to dunk her face again to get it to change, making the doll super wet again. Overall she is fun initially, but loses some of the extra appeal and is just a normal doll after the main color reveal is over.
customerReviews.reviewTitle: Fun initially, but then just like a normal doll

customerReviews.reviewText: [This review was collected as part of a promotion.] I received this product to and this is an honest review. My daughter(7) loves all the Color reveals and this one was no different! For starters it comes in a plastic tube to fill with water and reveal the doll, however with the new color series it only revealed the body of the doll unlike the others that reveal which doll you received. My daughter stated that she wishes the color reveal for this Barbie was like the other series and she didnt know which doll she had immediately opening the package, however to our surprise the reveal showed what scent the barbie would have! We received a cherry scent which smelled amazing! It also comes with the individual wrapped packages for the accessories(shoes,clothes,etc.). The Barbie has long hair with a color streak and my daughter said she wishes it came with a comb or brush in the accessories bag to style the hair as well. Overall she was very excited for the scent reveal Barbie and had it dressed and ready to hang out with her friends in the Barbie house!

Garbage dolls, garbage made. Terrible face paint, horribly made clothes, and got the same doll over and over, which would be cool if they were actually worth anything! Shame on Mattel . . . they need some new staff over there with better taste and should stop cutting corners!
